        <abstract>
            <p>Suggests FD call on Carl Semper.</p> 
<p>Inquires about <hi rend="italic">Porlieria</hi>: Do the leaves shut to check evaporation? Does it appear silver under water?</p> 
            <p>Explains how he thinks the pulvinus acts; wishes FD would investigate the point.</p>
        </abstract>
